    + add Dotty support
    + fix potential issue in RetrySet
    + add Scala 2.13 support (includes using new Collections API,
      changing all occurrences of deprecated ClassManifest for
      ClassTag)
    + disable "multi-barrier deadlock cycle" test (uses
      CommitBarrier)
